/*
* React Installation
    1) Install NodeJS and NPM.
    2) Install Visual studio code/Sublime/Atom/Brackets
    3) Install React from terminal 
        a: npm install -g create-react-app (to install react in global)
        b: npm uninstall -g create-react-app (to uninstall react in global)
        c: create-react-app --version (to check varsion)
        d: create-react-app <projectname> (to Environment Setup for folder)
        e: npx create-react-app <projectname> (to create app new ways)
    4) check through cmd
        -> node -v (to check version)
        -> npm -v (to check version)
*/

